      "visualKind": "shape",
      "title": "<h1>Instructions for Icebreaker: Create a Movie</h1><p>Put elements together into a cinematic masterpiece in this fun, creative team icebreaker! </p><p>This 3-step process will get everyone's creative juices flowing while building teamwork and presentation skills.</p><h2>Step 1: Add 1 Element for the Movie (10 minutes)</h2><p>Each team member will select a single element that must be featured in their movie concept.<br></p><p><strong>How to assign elements:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\">Fill your own sticky note with a movie element </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><strong>Element examples:</strong><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\">A kitchen knife</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">A loud bang</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Full moon night</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">An old photograph</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">A mysterious phone call</li></ol></li></ol><p></p><h2>Step 2: Create the Story (15 minutes)</h2><p>Participants develop together a storyline based entirely on their combined elements. <strong>Click <code>Run</code></strong> in the document from step 2, and see your movie creating live in the canvas.</p><h2>Step 3: Create Marketing Content (20 minutes)</h2><p>Transform your concept into promotional materials that would sell your movie to audiences.<br>Everything is done automatically once you kickstart step 2.</p><h2>Facilitator Tips</h2><p><strong>Preparation:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\">Assign each team member to a stick note.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Prepare a specific theme, if desired</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">Prepare examples of story elements, if desired.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\">You can also tweak the prompts in each component</li></ol><p><br><strong>During the Activity:</strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\">Use timers to avoid spending too much time on each step (5 minutes remaining, etc.)</li></ol>"
    },
